The Boot process 

Grub Menu -> Plymouth -> X Windowing System -> Display Manager/Login manager -> Desktop environment ( Which also includes Window manager)
Grub Menu -> Plymouth -> X Windowing System -> Display Manager/Login manager -> Window Mananager 
Grub Menu -> Plymouth -> X Windowing System -> Default Shell prompt 

Graphical Boot/Splash Screen: Plymouth


Canonical Ubuntu Booting Process
Boot Menu: Grub 2
Boot Screen: Plymouth https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bootsplash#FBSPLASH
Display Server: X11
Display Manager: Gnome Display Manager (gdm)
Desktop Environment: Gnome Shell
